name: High Volatility
description: High volatility scenario running on a short timescale. Price drifts for collateral assets are set to 0, and volatilities are set to their historical highs (p99 intraday volatility). Debt positions are randomly re-sampled from an empirical Gaussian KDE and crvUSD liquidity is randomly resampled from a multivariate Gaussian distribution. The sampled debt:liquidity ratio is centered around the historical average ratio.
